	      <article role="main">
		      		      	<div class="content">
	<h2>Proud of the quality, durability and value of our freezers and cold rooms</h2>
	<p>&nbsp;</p>
	<div class="container">
		 <div class="row">
            <section class="single-feature clearfix col-md-4 col-sm-6 ">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-sm-3 text-center feature-icon">
                       <i class="fa fa-cube" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-9">
                        <h5><a href="/coldrooms/">Coldrooms</a></h5>
                        <p>High quality modular or specially designed coldrooms. All manufactured in our own factory in Ossett. Coldrooms can be self assembled or by our techicians.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="single-feature clearfix col-md-4 col-sm-6 ">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-sm-3 text-center feature-icon">
                        <i class="fa fa-gitlab" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-9">
                        <h5><a href="/metal/">Metal Fabrication</a></h5>
                        <p>In house metal fabrication facility allows us to manufacture a variety of materials; Stainless steel, white foodsafe aluminium or galvanised steel.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <div class="visible-sm clearfix"></div>
            <section class="single-feature clearfix col-md-4 col-sm-6 ">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-sm-3 text-center feature-icon">
                        <i class="fa fa-building-o" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-9">
                        <h5><a href="/doors/">Doors</a></h5>
                        <p>High quality coldroom hinged doors hinged or sliding doors to cope with any temperature or environment.</p>
                        <p>&nbsp;</p>
                        <p>&nbsp;</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="single-feature clearfix col-md-4 col-sm-6 ">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-sm-3 text-center feature-icon">
                        <!-- <i class="fa fa-asterisk" aria-hidden="true"></i> -->
                        <i class="fa fa-server" aria-hidden="true"></i>                        
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-9">
                        <h5><a href="/insulate/">Fixings &amp; Insulation</a></h5>
                        <p>High quality premium cam-lock polyurethane panels in a variety of thicknesses. Foam injected complex components such as stainless steel sloping drain pans.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="single-feature clearfix col-md-4 col-sm-6 ">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-sm-3 text-center feature-icon">
                        <i class="fa fa-bars" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-9">
                        <h5><a href="/shelving/">Shelving</a></h5>
                        <p>Very popular - our shelving is high quality and great value. Modular anodised alloy shelving system with shelving inserts that can go in a dishwasher.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
            <section class="single-feature clearfix col-md-4 col-sm-6 ">
                <div class="row">
                    <div class="col-sm-3  text-center feature-icon">
                        <i class="fa fa-cogs" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col-sm-9">
                        <h5><a href="/spare-parts/">Parts, Spares &amp; Repairs</a></h5>
                        <p>Extensive range of parts and accessories in stock. Hinges, Fasteners, Heater Tape, Door Handles, Strip Curtains, Railings, Protector Plates, Adhesives and Sealants.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </section>
        </div>
     </div>       
